msgid "About"
msgstr "Tentang"

msgid ""
"KeePassRX is password manager for KeePass databases, designed for Ubuntu "
"Touch. It is licensed under the GNU AGPL v3 license."
msgstr ""
"KeePassRX adalah pengelola kata sandi untuk basis data KeePass, yang "
"dirancang untuk Ubuntu Touch. Aplikasi ini dilisensikan di bawah lisensi GNU "
"AGPL v3."

msgid ""
"The built-in KeePass icon images are licensed under a variety of licenses as "
"detailed in assets/COPYING."
msgstr ""
"Gambar ikon bawaan KeePass dilisensikan di bawah berbagai lisensi "
"sebagaimana dirinci dalam assets/COPYING."

